body.description: Why Choose Our Travel Luggage Organizer Bags? 1) Made of high-quality thicker polyester fabric (the new 290T double-sided twill fabric). Mesh top panel for easy identification of contents and well separate different clothes as you like. Light weight, washable. Durable & soft, easy to fold up, extremely portable, high performance for Waterproof and tear resistant. 2) With breathable mesh cloth, breathable, practical and beautiful, a better visibility ,find your things in a flash. 3) Come with 6 pieces different sizes of cubes/pouches ,can organize and separate your item, smooth material ensures that your clothes don't get creased. 4) Light travel is a pleasure, travel bags make you more convenient on the way! 5) Packing cubes a ideal gift for travellers, frequent flyer, casual camper, hiker, backpacker, friends or relatives. Packing List: - Large Mesh Cubes: 15.7"×11.8"×4.7", fit for sweaters, coats, jackets, blankets, bath towels or some big items. - Medium Mesh Cubes: 11.8"×11"×4.7", fit for dresses, T-shirts, pants or some Summer or Autumn clothes. - Small Mesh Cubes: 11.8"×7.9"×4.7", fit for T-shirts, shrits, bra, underpants, socks and some small items. - Underwear Bag: 11"×7.9" ×4.7", fit for: Put your bra underwear in the underwear bag so that you can find them easily. - Drawstring Bag: 13.8"×10.6", fit for: Seperate dirty clothes from clean clothes. - Flat Bag: 10.2"×5.9", fit for: personal digital items, socks or keys, cards, phone and cables and some small items. - Shoes Bag: 13.4"×8.3"×3.9", fit for: Keep your shoes separate from clothes,You can put a pair of sneakers or slippers.
